{
  "key": 29814,
  "messages": [
    {
      "id": "pl_msg_00000317_00000",
      "en_US": [
        "Cyrus: ...The shadowy Pokémon isn’t\n",
        "here.\r",
        "It abandoned me here, then disappeared\n",
        "somewhere farther down...\r",
        "Was it content merely to interfere\n",
        "with my plan...?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "pl_msg_00000317_00001",
      "en_US": "...If it’s true, you’ve impressed me.\r"
    },
    {
      "id": "pl_msg_00000317_00002",
      "en_US": "...No, of course, you wouldn’t.\r"
    },
    {
      "id": "pl_msg_00000317_00003",
      "en_US": [
        "The shadowy Pokémon must play a role in\n",
        "keeping the worlds in balance.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "pl_msg_00000317_00004",
      "en_US": [
        "That’s why trying to change our world\n",
        "disturbed it and made it reveal itself.\r",
        "But that is all irrelevant.\r",
        "What matters is defeating that Pokémon\n",
        "and making this world disappear.\r",
        "I won’t allow it to interfere with me\n",
        "again.\r",
        "With it gone, neither world will be able\n",
        "to revert to its original state...\r"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
